  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Companion Appearance Enhancement</span>. This articulated mining laser is insulated with a lightweight gel, ensuring ultimate comfort for companions assisting with resource harvesting.<br><br>Earn the trust of wild animals to adopt companions. Interact with companions to customise their appearance.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外观强化</span>。这种铰接式开采激光采用轻质凝胶隔热，能确保协助资源采集的同伴获得极致的舒适感。<br><br>赢得野生动物的信任来收养同伴。与同伴互动来自定义它们的外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外觀強化</span>。分節的採礦雷射，只有一層輕量的隔熱膠，為協助資源採收的同伴帶來最佳舒適享受。<br><br>獲得野生動物的信任，即可收養為同伴。與同伴互動，自訂其外觀。"
  },
